                        <interp inst="t18470510-name-197" type="given" value="JOHN"></interp>MR. JOHN FIELD</persName>
                  </hi>. These shillings are both counterfeit in all respects.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence.</hi> The shilling was one I took in change for half-a-crown, for a quarter of a pound of boiled beef the night before.</p>
